Ashford Hospitality Prime, Inc, et al v. Sessa Capital (Master), L.P., et al
                



Plaintiff - Appellee:
ASHFORD HOSPITALITY PRIME, INCORPORATED


Third Party Defendant - Appellee:
DOUGLAS A. KESSLER, ANDREW STRONG, STEFANI D. CARTER, CURTIS B. MCWILLIAMS, MONTY J. BENNETT, ASHFORD HOSPITALITY ADVISORS, L.L.C., ASHFORD, INCORPORATED, MATTHEW D. RINALDI and W. MICHAEL MURPHY


Defendant-Third Party Plaintiff - Appellant:
SESSA CAPITAL (MASTER), L.P.


Defendant - Appellant:
SESSA CAPITAL GP, L.L.C., SESSA CAPITAL IM, L.P., SESSA CAPITAL IM GP, L.L.C., JOHN E. PETRY, PHILIP B. LIVINGSTON, LAWRENCE A. CUNNINGHAM, DANIEL B. SILVERS and CHRIS D. WHEELER


Case Number:
16-10671


Filed:
May 25, 2016


Court:
U.S. Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit


Nature of Suit:
Securities, Commodities, Exchange




